<h1>Reservation Confirmed</h1>
<div class="divider"></div>

<p class="body-text">
    Dear <span class="accent">{{customerName}}</span>,<br><br>
    It is my honor to confirm your reservation. We are orchestrating every detail to ensure your gastronomic experience
    transcends the ordinary and becomes an indelible memory.
</p>

<div class="card">
    <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="label">Reservation</span>
        <span class="value">#{{reservationId}}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="label">Date & Time</span>
        <span class="value">{{date}} — {{time}}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="label">Guests</span>
        <span class="value">{{guests}} Guests</span>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-row">
        <span class="label">Location</span>
        <span class="value">{{location}}</span>
    </div>
</div>

<p class="body-text">
    Our team will contact you shortly to finalize your preferences and any special requirements.
</p>

<div style="text-align: center;">
    <p
        style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #ffffff;">
        Until soon,</p>
    <p style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: #D4AF37; text-transform: uppercase;">
        Federico Rodríguez</p>
</div>